<p class="wikiPara">
I've just uploaded the Seam 3.0.0.Beta2 bundled release to Sourceforge, where you can download it using the following link:
</p>

<p class="wikiPara">
<a href="http://sourceforge.net/projects/jboss/files/Seam/3/3.0.0.Beta2/seam-3.0.0.Beta2.zip/download" target="" class="regularLink">Download</a>
